<h2>Sounds</h2>
<div id="soundDiv">

<p>I have a long-standing fascination with sound: It's texture and it's shape, how it interacts with the environment, and how it interacts with itself.</p>  

<p>While making this site, I spent some time exploring the <a href="http://webaudio.github.io/web-audio-api/">Web Audio API</a> and created a simple tool for generating audible beats. I wanted to link to it but, well, it's not quite ready.</p>

<p>The Web Audio API is <span class="em">very</span> exciting.</p>

<p>Creating and manipulating audio and audio data in a web browser? Exciting. Creating the tools to do it? Very exciting.</p>

<p>Tools for real time collaboration? Tools for making personalized instruments and effects? Generative music based on Twitter feeds? I might find a way to incorporate this into a project.</p>
</div>

